Class TransmissionMessageConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • vehicle.TransmissionMessageConstants

  • public final class TransmissionMessageConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants class designated to keep set of RegularManualTransmission messages which will be returned depending upon the transmission actions.
